  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK912">
<l>payaṉṟūkkip paṇpuraikkum paṇpil makaḷir </l>
<l>nayaṉṟūkki naḷḷā viṭal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One must ascertain the character of the ill-natured women who after ascertaining the wealth (of a man) speak (as if they were) good natured-ones, and avoid intercourse (with them).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
